Usage: setMultiColorsHier [-help] [<colorID> [<hInstName>]]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<colorID>               # color Id to which all hierarchical instances or the
                        # specified hierarchical instance will be reset
                        # (int, optional, min=0, max=29)
<hInstName>             # name of hierarchical instance (string, optional)